  "source": [
   "## Concept: Operating Harness Agent\n",
   "\n",
   "A production harness is not one script \u2014 it is **subsystems composed**:\n",
   "\n",
   "| Subsystem | CLI |\n",
   "|-----------|-----|\n",
   "| Interactive use | `harness-agent chat` |\n",
   "| Messaging / automation ingress | `harness-agent gateway run` |\n",
   "| Scheduled agent jobs | `harness-agent cron tick` |\n",
   "| IDE integration | `harness-agent acp` |\n",
   "| Training data export | `harness-agent export-trajectories` |\n",
   "\n",
   "Compare to Hermes (many platforms, large tool surface) or OpenClaw (workspace-first). Harness Agent teaches the **architecture** you can extend.\n"
  ]
 },
 {
  "cell_type": "markdown",
  "metadata": {},
  "source": [
   "## How it works\n",
   "\n",
   "```mermaid\n",
   "flowchart TB\n",
   "  subgraph entries [Entry points]\n",
   "    CLI[chat]\n",
   "    GW[gateway]\n",
   "    CRON[cron]\n",
   "    ACP[acp]\n",
   "  end\n",
   "  entries --> AIAgent\n",
   "  AIAgent --> REG[Tool registry]\n",
   "  AIAgent --> DB[(SQLite sessions)]\n",
   "  AIAgent --> PROMPT[Prompt + skills + memory]\n",
   "```\n",
   "\n",
   "**Capstone checklist:**\n",
   "\n",
   "1. `harness-agent doctor` \u2014 green\n",
   "2. `harness-agent chat` \u2014 multi-turn with a tool\n",
   "3. `search_sessions` finds prior text\n",
   "4. Complex task creates a skill under `labs/skills/`\n",
   "5. `harness-agent export-trajectories` \u2014 JSONL\n",
   "6. `harness-agent cron tick` \u2014 job runs or reports API error clearly\n",
   "7. `discover_plugins()` loads `hello_plugin`\n"
  ]
 },
